snippet.title: Rocket Panda Launch Trailer -  A Delicious Rocket Adventure for Sega Genesis
snippet.description:
The evil Biscuit Head has invaded Biscuit Land, home of not just Rocket Panda but also his small furry band of Badgers. The Badgers have been kidnapped, and a menagerie of enemies have taken over the land, and it’s up to Rocket Panda to deftly fly to the rescue!

In this fun jetpack shooting adventure, assume the role of Rocket Panda as you guide him through a terrifyingly tasty world of dangerous mazes, looking out for Flying Pigs, Mines, Toasters, Tanks, and UFOs! Help Rocket Panda rescue Badgers that are hidden in the maze, who would follow our hero acting as limited shields!

Follow Rocket Panda on Kickstarter: https://bit.ly/RP-Kickstarter
More info on our website: https://bit.ly/MCSRocketPanda
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/megacat

Console Type: Sega Genesis/Mega Drive
Game Type: Thrust platformer
